239
00:13:12,631 --> 00:13:15,365
Là lí do tất cả
chuyện này xảy ra.

240
00:13:15,367 --> 00:13:16,900
Lí do tôi giết mẹ cô.

241
00:13:16,902 --> 00:13:19,302
Anh ấy chẳng cần giải thích.
Tự tôi cũng biết

242
00:13:19,304 --> 00:13:21,438
