243
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:25,175
Chà, dĩ nhiên là cậu ta không nói.

244
00:13:25,177 --> 00:13:27,678
Anh trai cậu rất thích
những bí mật.

245
00:13:29,881 --> 00:13:31,715
Lúc nào cũng thế.

246
00:13:31,717 --> 00:13:33,917
Con người cậu là vậy.

247
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:37,354
Nếu cậu nói với tôi những gì
thực sự xảy ra với Shado,

248
00:13:37,356 --> 00:13:38,855
mẹ cậu có thể vẫn còn sống.

249
00:13:38,857 --> 00:13:41,158
