00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:24,668
Anh vào chưa?

255
00:14:24,670 --> 00:14:26,303
Rồi.

256
00:14:28,539 --> 00:14:30,240
Rồi.

257
00:14:30,242 --> 00:14:31,508
Máy tính của công ty
được bảo mật

258
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:33,143
bằng mã hóa sinh học.

259
00:14:33,145 --> 00:14:34,978
Tìm máy đọc vân tay.

260
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:37,714
Sao họ không loại tôi
khỏi thư mục?

261
00:14:37,716 --> 00:14:40,217
Để làm gì?
Anh chết rồi mà.

262
00:14:50,595 --> 00:14:52,796
Ừ. Tôi vào rồi.

263
00:14:52,798 --> 00:14:56,233
Con rận được lập trình để truy cập
vào hệ thống mạng của Kang.

264
00:15:00,772 --> 00:15:03,974
Và nó đang chạy.

265
00:15:03,976 --> 00:15:07,077
Chương trình sẽ tốn 90 giây.

266
00:15:12,150 --> 00:15:14,084
Cái gì vậy?

267
00:15:35,406 --> 00:15:37,974
Oliver, cậu phải ra khỏi đó.

268
00:15:37,976 --> 00:15:40,443
Tôi chưa xong.

269
00:15:48,619 --> 00:15:50,821
Ra khỏi đó ngay.
Có người đang đến.

270
00:16:09,907 --> 00:16:12,209
Anh dễ thương đấy.

271
00:16:14,045 --> 00:16:16,346
Chỉ có điều là anh chết rồi.

272
00:16:16,348 --> 00:16:20,350
Dĩ nhiên là bất lợi cho anh
hơn là cho tôi.

273
00:16:20,352 --> 00:16:23,053
Mình phải học cách

274
00:16:23,055 --> 00:16:26,456
thôi không nói chuyện
một mình nữa.

275
00:16:29,060 --> 00:16:31,194
Theo như thông tin chúng ta
lấy được từ máy tính của Kang,

276
00:16:31,196 --> 00:16:33,463
buổi đấu giá diễn ra hôm nay.

277
00:16:33,465 --> 00:16:35,165
- Trong bốn tiếng nữa.
- Ở đâu?

278
00:16:35,167 --> 00:16:36,533
Họ vẫn đang tìm hiểu.

279
00:16:36,535 --> 00:16:37,868
Chương trình con rận

280
00:16:37,870 --> 00:16:39,803
lấy về 2.7 gigabyte dữ liệu.

281
00:16:39,805 --> 00:16:41,605
Phải mất một thời gian
để lọc ra.

282
00:16:41,607 --> 00:16:44,474
Dĩ nhiên, anh có ít hơn bốn tiếng.

283
00:16:44,476 --> 00:16:46,309
Queen đâu?

284
00:16:48,379 --> 00:16:51,514
Chắc là đi kiểm tra vũ khí.

285
00:16:52,783 --> 00:16:56,286
♪ You spin my head
right round ♪

286
00:16:56,288 --> 00:17:00,790
